title: International Trade Administration, Total Arrivals - Canada and Mexico and All Non-Resident Arrivals by month, USA, 2007
name: International Trade Administration, Total Arrivals - Canada and Mexico and All Non-Resident Arrivals by month, USA, 2007
description:
This dataset explores the number of non-resident arrivals to the United States in 2007 by month. The counts provide a look at the number of people coming into the country by month from the two bordering neighbors - Mexico and Canada. 

* ARRIVALS TO INTERIOR ONLY (SEE INTRODUCTION).
